creator: Marco Studios
descriptionHtml:
Yes or No is a fun and addicting game, perfect for playing on your own or with friends/family.

This game contains hundreds of the best hand picked Yes or No questions.

Vote which option you would rather choose and view real time statistics on what option was the most popular.

★★ Features ★★
✔ Hundreds of Yes or No questions
✔ Frequently updated with more content
✔ Submit your own Yes or No questions
✔ Completely free to play
✔ View real time statistics on what option (Yes or No) was more popular
✔ Family friendly questions making it the perfect app for all ages.

Answer questions such as:
- Have you ever had a dream that came true?
- Do you like the game Would You Rather?
- Have you never been to a concert?
- Do you like making people laugh?
- True or false?
- Have you ever used a dating app before?
- Have you ever play the game Truth or Dare before?

An internet connection is required to play this game.

In this game you are totally anonymous. The only thing saved is how many people voted for each answer.

What option would you rather pick? Play now to find out!

Feedback is always appreciated

Yes or No is a funny and addicting questions game to play when you are bored.

This game contains hundreds of the best and challenging Yes or No questions. Can you pick the most popular option?

★★ Features ★★
✔ Hundreds of fun, addicting and funny Yes or No questions
✔ Submit your own fun Yes or No questions
✔ Addicting game with tons of questions
✔ Funny game to play with your best BFF friends
✔ Fun game for both boys and girls to play and pass time when you are bored
✔ View real time statistics on what option (Yes or No) was more popular
✔ No adult questions making it the best game to play with the family

In this game you are totally anonymous. The only thing saved is how many people voted for each answer to see which option is most popular. You can skip any Yes or No questions you do not want to answer.

If you are bored, this is the best game aimed at both boys and girls to cure you of boredom.

It’s very easy to play. All you need to do is read the question and then click ‘Yes’ or ‘No’. After you vote you can see statistics on which challenging option was more popular.

We hope you enjoy playing our funny and addicting game to pass time. What would you rather choose? Have fun voting for your most popular option!
descriptionShort: A big & funny game of Yes or No questions. Find out which option is most popular
